songs.title: Fvcking Pessimist
songs.lyrics:
Time goes by
And you begin to realize that life is not a fairy tale

The reality account is an endless story
Our souls will want a happy story

The happy for "always" if it exists but in the mind of the pessimistic imbecile

You will realize that you are not a princess imprisoned in your tower

You're just locked in your mind about to cease to exist

The reality account is an endless story
Our souls will want a happy story

The only person who can save you is you
Because life is not a fairy tale
It's a horror movie

You're just locked in your mind about to cease to exist


You'll be fine, promise, but ...
DO NOT BE SO PESIMIST
